The paper deals with the problem of efficient geometrical verification in UAV image matching, which involves computer vision, robotics, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses UAV flight control data and camera mounting angles, which suggests that it may belong to cs.RO (Robotics). The paper deals with spatial relationships and motion consistency, which suggests that it may belong to cs.GR (Graphics). The paper also uses a voting scheme, which suggests that it may belong to cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper proposes a strategy for efficient geometrical verification, which suggests that it may belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning).
